  "texts": [
    "To ensure the high quality of pseudo-labels, we calibrate their distribution so that it aligns with the distribution of the actual ground truth labels.",
    "The first operation is multiplication of the predicted and ground truth distributions: This step enhances the parts of the predicted distribution that match the ground truth distribution.",
    "If a certain class has a high probability in both the predicted and ground truth distributions, its probability will further increase after multiplication.",
    "Conversely, if a class has a high probability in the predicted distribution but a low probability in the ground truth distribution, its probability will decrease after multiplication.",
    "Let _ p 2 R C be the prediction of the pseudo-label of one unlabeled instance."
  ],
